## Lab 10: Multilevel Modeling

For this lab, we will apply core concepts from class to a dataset from Coyne et al. (2019). Here, you will fit, interpret, and visualize results from a multilevel model.

> Coyne, M. D., McCoach, D. B., Ware, S., Austin, C. R., Loftus-Rattan, S. M., & Baker, D. L. (2019). Racing Against the Vocabulary Gap: Matthew Effects in Early Vocabulary Instruction and Intervention. *Exceptional Children*, *85*(2), 163--179. <https://doi.org/10.1177/0014402918789162>

To access Lab 10, please [click here](https://classroom.github.com/a/GUBRA5g4).
